{"id":302571,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-成都李廷惠等访民状告公安局非法羁押案7/","date":"2013-07-07T06:48:22Z","modified":"2013-07-07T06:48:22Z","title":"维权网 | 成都李廷惠等访民状告公安局非法羁押案7月9日开庭（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员陈华报道）成都访民李廷惠等四位公民状告公安局非法羁押案，将于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>在锦江区法院第一法庭开庭，因案情相似，且被告均为锦江区公安局，案件合并审理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>根据有关法律规定，每位原告可委托</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>名公民代理，届时由四名原告加上各自委托的两名公民代理，将会有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>名公民组成阵容庞大的原告团。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>就李廷惠一个人来说就有四桩“行政拘留处罚”，其中一桩就是李廷惠身穿“找清官”文化衫在闹市打快板，引来无数市民围观，后被当地公安驱散，并以“扰乱社会治安”对李廷惠行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>四桩行政拘留案，李廷惠都在相应的时间对锦江公安局提出了行政诉讼而被拖延无结果，此次“合并审理”引起当地上访维权人士的极大关注，法院能否公正审理，也直接关乎到上访群体的人身自由权及信访权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>审理在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>分</span><span>在晋江法院第一法庭开始逐一审理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BcJnfdqcOzc/UdjZC81DS-I/AAAAAAAAk54/MgECG2xQ_EY/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BcJnfdqcOzc/UdjZC81DS-I/AAAAAAAAk54/MgECG2xQ_EY/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"220\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wkKOzOsc5Hg/UdjZD26ttCI/AAAAAAAAk6A/Jp4NNMtJEwI/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-wkKOzOsc5Hg/UdjZD26ttCI/AAAAAAAAk6A/Jp4NNMtJEwI/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\" width=\"237\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oUTjptVE_Wo/UdjZFgaaT3I/AAAAAAAAk6I/p1Q44dYsZT4/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"271\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-oUTjptVE_Wo/UdjZFgaaT3I/AAAAAAAAk6I/p1Q44dYsZT4/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OOVkKG4phl4/UdjZGlRI9XI/AAAAAAAAk6Q/c16Um3x3PPk/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE03.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"215\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OOVkKG4phl4/UdjZGlRI9XI/AAAAAAAAk6Q/c16Um3x3PPk/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE03.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}